    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout. The body, paint, interior, and trim all show the kind of careful preservation and attention buyers hope to find in a top-quality car, with a clean, highly detailed appearance inside and out. This is not a project or a rough driver\u2014it\u2019s a standout example that should appeal to collectors or anyone wanting a well-kept, show-ready car they can be proud to own. Expect a very strong overall presentation with only the most minor age-appropriate signs of use, if any.",
