      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into ownership for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking basic transportation, a project, or a practical work car, it presents a solid value opportunity at an accessible price. Priced to sell and represented honestly, this is a straightforward deal for shoppers who recognize potential.",
