    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Reliable, affordable, and ready for its next owner. This is a straightforward budget-friendly car that\u2019s been a dependable way to get around and still has plenty to offer someone looking for inexpensive transportation. It\u2019s not perfect, but if you want honest value and a vehicle you can drive without spending a fortune, this is a great opportunity. Priced fairly and presented by a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to work with.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with a strong-running powertrain, smooth-shifting transmission, and dependable core mechanicals. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but it\u2019s a straightforward platform with good bones and plenty of usable life left for someone who wants affordable transportation or a weekend fixer. Starts up, moves out well, and offers a great entry point for an enthusiast looking for value without paying premium-market money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
