      "description": "A car with honest character and a story in every mile, this one has the kind of presence that turns a simple drive into something memorable. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who appreciates a machine with personality\u2014perfect as a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a practical second vehicle. Distinctive, approachable, and full of potential, it offers the chance to make it your own while enjoying the simple satisfaction of getting behind the wheel of something real.",
